Package: opencog-atomspace-pgres
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, opencog-atomspace, python3, postgresql-client
Description: PostgreSQL storage backend for OpenCog AtomSpace
 This package provides a PostgreSQL-backed persistent storage system for the
 OpenCog AtomSpace hypergraph database. It enables distributed and scalable
 storage of knowledge graphs with full ACID compliance.
 .
 Features include:
  - High-performance bulk loading and retrieval
  - Distributed storage across multiple PostgreSQL instances
  - Full transaction support
  - Query optimization for hypergraph patterns
  - Automatic schema management
 .
 This backend is suitable for production deployments requiring robust
 persistence and multi-user access to large knowledge bases.
